Package tiles.propagation

This package contains the available propagation components for use by the tiles.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
BlockPropagation Propagation component that blocks all rays.
DoubleMirrorPropagation Propagation component that reflects rays in every direction.
FilterPropagation Propagation component that filters the incoming ray color.
IgnorePropagation Propagation component that lets ray pass without bothering them.
MirrorPropagation Propagation component that changes the direction of the ray in a mirrored way.
PropagationComponent The base propagation component that defines public methods and encapsulates access to tile state in subclasses.
SplitMirrorPropagation Propagation component that lets rays continue in the direction they came from but also reflects them like a mirror.
 

Package tiles.propagation Description

This package contains the available propagation components for use by the tiles.
